{
  "name": "w06_e01_01.ks",
  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "line": "翌日から、絵麻と二人でさっそく同好会員集めを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "line": "はじめることにした。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "line": "「ん……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "line": "本日最後の授業が終わり、絵麻を迎えに行くために、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "line": "いそいそと帰り支度をしていると、にわかに教室の後方が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "line": "騒がしくなった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "line": "「なんだ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM050001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "line": "「すごい人だかりができてるわね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "line": "後方のドア付近に人があふれて、さながらスターが\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "line": "来日した空港のようになっている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "line": "「おい、和哉、来いよっ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "line": "人だまりから飛び出してきた十兵衛が、なにやら\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "line": "興奮気味に俺を手招きする。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "line": "「いや、人が多すぎて近づけないよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "line": "そこまでミーハーな根性は持ち合わせていないし、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "line": "絵麻を迎えに行くことが今は最優先だ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050002\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "line": "「なに言ってんだ、絵麻ちゃんが来てるんだよ、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "line": "　絵麻ちゃんが！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "line": "「なにいっっっ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "line": "俺はかばんを机に放り投げて、きゃいきゃいと黄色い声を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "line": "あげている生徒たちをかきわけ、中心へとたどり着く。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "line": "「絵麻っ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "line": "「お……お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "line": "人の輪の中心には、今にも倒れそうな青い顔でドアに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "line": "もたれている絵麻の姿があった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM050002\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "line": "「あっ、本当に絵麻じゃない」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 125,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "line": "俺のあとに続いたらしい智花が、隣に立って目を丸くする。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 132,
      "line": "「一体どうしたんだ、こんなところまで来るなんて\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 133,
      "line": "　珍しいじゃないか」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 139,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050002\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃんを、迎えにきました」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 143,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 144,
      "line": "取り囲んでいる生徒たちの声にかき消されてしまいそうな\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 145,
      "line": "ほど、ひどくか細い声だった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 151,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM050003\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 152,
      "line": "「迎えに来たって、絵麻ひとりで？　弥恵はどうしたの？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 157,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050003\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 158,
      "line": "「お姉ちゃんは、いずみお姉ちゃんのところに行きました」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 164,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 165,
      "line": "「いずみ姉さんのところ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 171,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050004\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 172,
      "line": "「はい、分担です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 178,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179,
      "line": "きっと、昨晩の役割分担のことを言っているのだろう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 182,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 183,
      "line": "受け答えをしている間にも、絵麻はふらふらと身体を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 184,
      "line": "揺らしていて、どんどん顔色が悪くなっていく。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 187,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 188,
      "line": "「移動しようか、絵麻」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 194,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195,
      "line": "俺は絵麻のことを抱きかかえた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 202,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050005\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 203,
      "line": "「ふわっ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 206,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 207,
      "line": "「じゃあ、また家でな、智花」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 213,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM050004\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 214,
      "line": "「えっ、ええ……お店の準備はしておくわね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 217,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 218,
      "line": "「ありがとう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 221,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 222,
      "line": "俺の行動にあっけにとられている智花を置いて、俺は\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 223,
      "line": "教室をあとにした。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 234,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050006\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 235,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 242,
      "line": "抱きかかえたままの絵麻が、ちょこちょこと肩口を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 243,
      "line": "引っ張ってくる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 247,
      "line": "「どうした？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 252,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050007\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253,
      "line": "「かばんはどうしたのですか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 256,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 257,
      "line": "「あ……まあ、あとで取りに行くよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 261,
      "line": "あの喧噪の中へ、絵麻を連れたまま戻る気にはなれない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 265,
      "line": "……というか、また注目を集めてしまっている気がする。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 268,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 269,
      "line": "さすがにこの年の女の子を抱っこして歩くのは、いくら\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 270,
      "line": "兄妹でも不自然か。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 276,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050008\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 277,
      "line": "「あ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 280,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 281,
      "line": "絵麻を下ろすと、絵麻が名残惜しそうな声を出した。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 284,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 285,
      "line": "「それにしても、どうしてあんなに囲まれてたんだ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 288,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 289,
      "line": "照れ紛れに問いかけると、絵麻は普段通りの平坦な表情に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 290,
      "line": "戻って首を傾げた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 296,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050009\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 297,
      "line": "「えまにはわかりません、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 307,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050003\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 308,
      "line": "「その疑問には俺が答えよう！！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 315,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 316,
      "line": "「うわ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 321,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 322,
      "line": "突然横合いから十兵衛が声をかけてきた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 325,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 326,
      "line": "「驚かせるなよ、十兵衛……絵麻が怯えるだろう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 332,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050004\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 333,
      "line": "「悪い悪い、ほら、かばんを持って来てやったんだから、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 334,
      "line": "　許してくれ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 337,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 338,
      "line": "「おお、わざわざ持って来てくれたのか、ありがとう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 341,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 342,
      "line": "「それで、十兵衛には人だかりの理由が分かってるのか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 347,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050005\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 348,
      "line": "「分かってるというか、分かってないのは当人たちだけ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 349,
      "line": "　なんじゃないか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 352,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 353,
      "line": "「……どういうことだ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 356,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 357,
      "line": "訳知り顔で頷いている十兵衛に問いかけると、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 358,
      "line": "わざとらしい吐息が返ってきた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 370,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050006\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 371,
      "line": "「絵麻ちゃんがかわいいからに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 372,
      "line": "　決まってるだろ！！！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 377,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 378,
      "line": "「はあ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 384,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050007\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 385,
      "line": "「な、なんだ、人類の敵を見るようなその目は！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 388,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 389,
      "line": "「今までありがとう十兵衛、お前がかばんを持って来て\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 390,
      "line": "　くれたことは一生忘れない」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 396,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050008\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 397,
      "line": "「俺との思い出がそれだけだったみたいな言い方だな！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 400,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 401,
      "line": "「十兵衛がしょうもないことを言うからだろう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 407,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050009\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 408,
      "line": "「事実なんだから仕方ないだろ。前から言ってたじゃ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 409,
      "line": "　ないか、弥恵ちゃんと絵麻ちゃんは１年の中でも\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 410,
      "line": "　トップクラスの美少女なんだって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 413,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 414,
      "line": "「それ、冗談じゃなかったのか……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 420,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050010\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 421,
      "line": "「いずみさんを筆頭に、お前ら姉弟は美形揃いで有名\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 422,
      "line": "　だからな。しかも絵麻ちゃんはめったに教室から\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 423,
      "line": "　出てこないレアキャラだし」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 426,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 427,
      "line": "「人の妹に失礼な表現を使うな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 433,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050011\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 434,
      "line": "「ぅぅ、すまん。本当に溺愛してるんだな、和哉……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 437,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 438,
      "line": "ちょっと人前に出るだけで酸欠を起こしてしまうような\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 439,
      "line": "か弱い女の子なのだから、大切にするのは当然だ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 442,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 443,
      "line": "というか、俺の幼馴染みだと分かっている十兵衛とでさえ、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 444,
      "line": "会話に参加しようともせず俺にしがみついている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 450,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050012\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 451,
      "line": "「どっちかっていうと親子みたいだなぁ、お前たち」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 454,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 455,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 458,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 459,
      "line": "確かに自分でも、絵麻に対する過保護っぷりは兄妹の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 460,
      "line": "度を超えているような気がしている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 463,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 464,
      "line": "だからと言って、今の行動を変えるつもりは全くないが。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 471,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050010\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 472,
      "line": "「おやこ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 475,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 476,
      "line": "なにやら琴線に触れたらしく、絵麻がぴくりと反応する。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 483,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050011\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 484,
      "line": "「……お父さん？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 487,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 488,
      "line": "小首を傾げながらささやくように言われて、少し\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 489,
      "line": "きゅんときてしまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 492,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 493,
      "line": "しかし『お父さん』はやっぱりまだ微妙だな……むしろ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 494,
      "line": "せっかくなら……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 499,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 500,
      "line": "……………………\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 503,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 504,
      "line": "せっかくなら……なんだろう？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 507,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 508,
      "line": "自分で連想したことだというのに、はたと思考が止まって\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 509,
      "line": "しまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 517,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050013\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 518,
      "line": "「うおおおおおおお、レア発言きたああああああああ！！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 524,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050012\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 525,
      "line": "「ひゃくっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 531,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050014\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 532,
      "line": "「俺に向けてじゃなくていいから、もう一回聞かせてくれ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 533,
      "line": "　ないかな、絵麻ちゃん！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 536,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 537,
      "line": "「言わせるわけがないだろう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 547,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 548,
      "line": "絵麻を隠すように、十兵衛に背を向ける。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 555,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050013\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 556,
      "line": "「あう……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 563,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050015\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 564,
      "line": "「保護者がそう言うなら仕方ないか……それじゃいまの\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 565,
      "line": "　出来事をさっそく同好の士に伝えてくることにしよう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 568,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 569,
      "line": "「あ、おい……っ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 575,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB050016\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 576,
      "line": "「じゃあな和哉、絵麻ちゃん！　ごちそうさま！！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 582,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 583,
      "line": "いろいろと突っ込みどころの多い発言を投げっぱなしに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 584,
      "line": "して、十兵衛は元来た道を去って行った。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 589,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 590,
      "line": "あの怪しげな同好会に絵麻のことを吹聴されるのは\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 591,
      "line": "気にくわないが、追いかけていって余計話題を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 592,
      "line": "提供するのもしゃくに思える。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 597,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050014\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 598,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん、どうしましたか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 601,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 602,
      "line": "廊下で立ち止まった俺を見下ろし、絵麻が首を傾げる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 605,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 606,
      "line": "「いや、なんでもない……とりあえず、どこか落ち着いて\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 607,
      "line": "　話せる場所に行った方がいいな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 619,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 620,
      "line": "絵麻の体調が不安だったこともあり、俺たちは保健室へと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 621,
      "line": "やってきた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 629,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050015\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 630,
      "line": "「んしょ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 633,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 634,
      "line": "保健の先生はいなかったが、絵麻は慣れた様子で窓際の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 635,
      "line": "ベッドへと座る。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 638,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 639,
      "line": "「特等席なんだな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 645,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050016\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 646,
      "line": "「『いつもの』です、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 649,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 650,
      "line": "絵麻がこくりと頷いた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 653,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 654,
      "line": "絵麻の身体が弱いのは把握しているが、そんなに通って\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 655,
      "line": "いるとは気付かなかった。以前よりは通う回数は減って\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 656,
      "line": "いたと思っていたのに……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 659,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 660,
      "line": "「なにかあったら、必ず俺にも言ってくれよ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 665,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050017\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 666,
      "line": "「分かりました」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 671,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 672,
      "line": "素直に頷いている絵麻の正面に椅子を置いて座り、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 673,
      "line": "顔をのぞきこむ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 678,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 679,
      "line": "「……うん、大丈夫みたいだな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 685,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050018\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 686,
      "line": "「はい、心配をかけてごめんなさい、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 689,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 690,
      "line": "「絵麻が謝るようなことじゃないよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 696,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 697,
      "line": "頭をなでると、絵麻は嬉しそうにもじもじとした。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 700,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 701,
      "line": "「先生もいないし、ここで今日のことを話し合おうか」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 707,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050019\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 708,
      "line": "「はい、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 711,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 712,
      "line": "絵麻がこくりと頷いた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 717,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 718,
      "line": "「とりあえず、絵麻はどんな人に会員になってほしいん\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 719,
      "line": "　だ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 725,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050020\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 726,
      "line": "「んう……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 729,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 730,
      "line": "途端に、絵麻は難しい顔をして俯いてしまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 733,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 734,
      "line": "「昨日はみこと姉ちゃんのことを断っていただろう？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 735,
      "line": "　つまりは、理想の人物像があるってことだよな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 741,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 742,
      "line": "絵麻はこくりと頷き、ガラス玉のような瞳で俺を見つめた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 747,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050021\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 748,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 751,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 752,
      "line": "「うん？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 758,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050022\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 759,
      "line": "「理想は、お兄ちゃんです」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 762,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 763,
      "line": "「……そう言ってくれるのは嬉しいんだけどな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 766,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 767,
      "line": "そして、入会してやりたいのも山々なのだが、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 768,
      "line": "立場上簡単なことではない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 771,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 772,
      "line": "「俺以外だったら、どんな人がいいのか聞かせてもらえる\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 773,
      "line": "　か？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 779,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050023\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 780,
      "line": "「んん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 783,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 784,
      "line": "俺はしょんぼりとしている絵麻の顔をのぞき込み、質問を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 785,
      "line": "重ねることにした。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 788,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 789,
      "line": "「例えば、学年の希望はあるのか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 792,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 793,
      "line": "「３年生はすぐ引退してしまうから嫌だって言ってたよな？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 794,
      "line": "　それじゃあ２年生ならいいのか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 800,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050024\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 801,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃんじゃないなら、２年生でもだめです」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 804,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 805,
      "line": "「そ、そうか……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 808,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 809,
      "line": "兄冥利に尽きる言葉ではあるが、今は感動している場合で\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 810,
      "line": "はない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 813,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 814,
      "line": "「それじゃあ１年生がいいよな、同い年だし」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 820,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050025\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 821,
      "line": "「んうぅ……はい……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 824,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 825,
      "line": "不服そうながら、絵麻が頷いた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 828,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 829,
      "line": "「じゃあ、性別は……っと、これは聞くまでもないか」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 834,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050026\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 835,
      "line": "「……男の子」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 838,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 839,
      "line": "「え？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 845,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050027\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 846,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん以外の男の子は、いやです」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 849,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 850,
      "line": "「そ、そうか」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 853,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 854,
      "line": "一瞬、男がいいと言ったのかと、ひやりとしてしまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 857,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 858,
      "line": "「まあ、お菓子作りっていう時点で、よほど趣味で\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 859,
      "line": "　やってない限りは、男は除外になるよなぁ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 864,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050028\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 865,
      "line": "「……お兄ちゃんはいやですか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 868,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 869,
      "line": "「俺は『よほど』の方だな。昔から店を手伝ってるし」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 875,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050029\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 876,
      "line": "「そうですか」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 879,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 880,
      "line": "絵麻がしごくほっとしたような顔をする。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 883,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 884,
      "line": "その表情を見ていると、今すぐにでも生徒会を辞めて\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 885,
      "line": "お菓子作り同好会の三人目になりたくなってしまう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 888,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 889,
      "line": "「と……とりあえず、１年生の女の子だな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 895,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050030\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 896,
      "line": "「んうぅ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 899,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 900,
      "line": "俺の言葉に、絵麻は難しい顔をした。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 903,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 904,
      "line": "「なにかいやなのか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 909,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050031\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 910,
      "line": "「同好会にも、部活動監査はありますか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 913,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 914,
      "line": "「あるにはあるぞ。同好会だって部活と同じく生徒活動の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 915,
      "line": "　一環なんだから」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 918,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 919,
      "line": "答えて初めて、それなら俺がいつでもお菓子作り同好会の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 920,
      "line": "様子を見に行くことができると気付いた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 926,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050032\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 927,
      "line": "「それなら、女の子もだめです」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 930,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 931,
      "line": "「え？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 939,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 940,
      "line": "絵麻は拗ねた表情をして、ぎゅうっと俺の服を掴んだ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 943,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 944,
      "line": "「それならどんな子ならいいんだ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 950,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050033\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 951,
      "line": "「んぅぅぅ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 954,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 955,
      "line": "「もう一人いないと、同好会を作れないぞ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 961,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM050034\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 962,
      "line": "「んぅぅ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 965,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 966,
      "line": "同好会を作るための行動を起こすようになるなんて、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 967,
      "line": "積極的に変わったものだと思っていたのだが、いきなり\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 968,
